Description:
-------------
    - The main purpose of this script is to run CPU stress tests using the
      stress-ng program.

Input Parameters:
-------------------
    --runtime <time-in-seconds>
    
    The total runtime, if not specified, is defaulted to 7200 seconds
    i.e 2 hours.

Usage:
--------
    cpu_stress --runtime <time-in-seconds>
    
List of stressors used - 
--------------------------
        - af-alg 
        - bsearch 
        - context 
        - cpu
        - crypt
        - hsearch
        - longjmp
        - lsearch
        - matrix
        - qsort
        - str
        - stream
        - tsearch
        - vecmath
        - wcs
